{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Your AI agent is bleeding tokens. Right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:94c39deee7d27f17be1094bb33a09d67d58fe8031d6afe9856d319d22abfefa2",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here's the proof: it just flagged a string of text as a real bug, in quotes, on line two-eight-one-three.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c5aa2946e36c3b263c471dc67217eed9b979415412e38c81b6f28ac064c0ca9",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 7.476825396825397,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Then it billed you to investigate. There's a smarter search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e38f6deca67a074093e7e2373bd954e56d6f9628ed93f2d500bfcd75bc966c77",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Your agent doesn't have it yet. Every AI coding agent has the same blind spot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:20478b182b5664719b9ef1110ad8d19526cf9a420e8c755508d241b02b5c50df",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 37
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Claude Code, Cursor, Copilot \u2014 they all search your code the same dumb way.",
      "checksum": "sha256:67a0e89c141a8a3f8a8307bb1c00ff354b31f2a79b7d0f6d93a9695ff0cbc34e",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 52
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "They scan for matching text. That's it. They can't tell the difference between code that actually runs and a string that just looks like code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:61eb993e23295949ad5e382cdccf8c741f59ba40d55f2edba0dad328d8ef5691",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 9.009342403628118,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Watch what that costs you. Meet ast-grep.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9d849714dbb362746fb1e129ad6f56870641cb9a6c6425ac9cea979eff744459",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 91
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "It's a smarter search tool that reads your code as code \u2014 not as a wall of text.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f21366c06a71d226d2e0dd18eb8ce5f72fc50026f34f64e67b442a6ec069a966",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "A regular search sees characters. ast-grep sees structure: functions, calls, try-catch blocks, the real shape of what you wrote.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cbc39682867fe44a91ee0a6306fbe62d6e5b24661ec6f26612ba04b6a3d23462",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.544943310657596,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 116
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "You hand it to your agent in one config line.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0dfdca22247499c59199b761b41b94bc77896200ab1c6524b7e9e6532ea2fe5b",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 135
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Now your agent stops getting fooled. And stops billing you for the cleanup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0ef3762c5cb52fb12fb394c3c497c5da33adc60f1103859a2956e9340287119d",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 145
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Watch your agent waste your money. You ask it to clean up debug logs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f745b9142cab2b47accd93af36dc13996a5209d3124b6870d031ea253cfdf419",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 158
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "With the dumb text search, the agent finds 164 matches across 22 files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:69bf9ea70de031eb285687996348667858d8b8dca89038170b8e7f91e1a16971",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 172
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "It opens every one. But here's what's hiding inside dag-executor dot test dot ts line two-eight-one-three: a test fixture passes the literal string console-dot-log-hi.",
      "checksum": "sha256:18de0f2f018bfda5f58f55983607ab59f2393f520ba2ab8c646b0644e2b8c934",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 11.470657596371883,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 185
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "It's not a real call. It's just quoted text.",
      "checksum": "sha256:32b0314f5559c536f4c8a7adfbe75e99c7691017e759cd3892db01a7a4492c40",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 209
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The agent reads the whole file, triages it, and bills you. ast-grep skips it instantly.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0c8608aeb9e5aff5769e6b7ff0854f2de6be0129dcd0856f98caba036f86aea",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 218
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Twelve files, not twenty-two. One example isn't a pattern.",
      "checksum": "sha256:212dbb3561871e60f74a5b85a07a46124a35719b193b6b67bdbdb1a03d88f1cc",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 233
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "So we tested five common searches on the same codebase.",
      "checksum": "sha256:86523971118a2ff2828622cd606e2df23538483763d9a0373fa67d0a0769f0a1",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 242
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "The dumb search over-counted by twenty-six percent on debug logs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ed682cdf4761eb4a90b7a0580cd7baf75d0a34d1ff320fa0f14828146cc14f7f",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 252
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Nineteen percent on setTimeout. Thirty percent on promise chains.",
      "checksum": "sha256:85589319486c6a552ed6fbfebe83afe9a62bcf6a8b4df897ef02d438f3a95d91",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 262
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "One-hundred-and-twenty-two percent on useState hooks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1803711ad4785faa6c239740dd3407a608a45bfac57262af2cb7bb9fbbe7fa02",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 271
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "That's pure billed waste. Every false hit is a file your agent has to open, scan, and pay for. ast-grep cuts it in half.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8c667a7a36f1f4e858bfb4591c788c8361fdb9dceddb608131c0eb33e9a2469a",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 7.1053061224489795,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 276
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Quick word from our affiliate, Hostinger.",
      "checksum": "sha256:74bad3e8093a66c8b2e7c373fee7ff398233efd4796821145855ee3e5a890e29",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 300
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "If you're spinning up your own AI agents or coding sandboxes, Hostinger gives you 10 percent off with the code D I Y smartcode in the description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:359ff94cd1c496acf0774452874dbda57e7d2a880946cbe14170c5738357a849",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 9.195102040816327,
      "word_count": 27,
      "words_offset": 306
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Now, back to ast-grep. Let's translate that into money.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a1978e06494b61b02a05e2185be18efa56551cc9d3af215d65234d7c6833c39b",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 333
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "To audit those 22 files, your agent has to open 22 files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e15f75c755985b28518c50c9ad47e1a1041f774a442be19f3307cf2e6143f9e",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 342
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "That's roughly eleven thousand tokens of context \u2014 call it a cent for a single refactor.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c1cbc14b5987005eb69c7ab57d095525dacf5f17be563808b412627d807dd594",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 354
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Now scale it up. If your team runs fifty refactors a day, thirty days a month, that cent becomes fifteen dollars of pure waste, per developer, just on bad search. ast-grep does the same job in one structured query.",
      "checksum": "sha256:227752aeb1128216a5af1ec1558b3fb5dd93454ae3277c703c9e86f56d4bd567",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 14.582131519274377,
      "word_count": 39,
      "words_offset": 370
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Roughly half the tokens. Your agent stops re-reading files it shouldn't have opened.\n\nBut my agent already has search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a67821598606148a17f8dc71b42b4b032376f37cbc6aa71fce6776736bd6a1cf",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 7.198185941043084,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 409
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Yes \u2014 and it's the dumb one. But Claude Code has Read and Glob.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9429d89ab335626309109609ab4dbb7807b9ef2afc00e064d6fb8efa9a7df1eb",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 428
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Different jobs. Read opens a file you point at.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3ea5e7eb439bdfb788f9127af212859ac6ab08010e64768e0ff5dc35f84ebdb0",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 442
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Glob lists files by name. Neither one understands code structure.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ddd7d680e7784829debed9e1b79b33a8013f6c813dcaf1b6517c9061dd3e8813",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 451
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "That's what ast-grep adds. But this sounds technical.",
      "checksum": "sha256:35b367777e57c91ac4fe5a1142f50d9c01a1d1f8c514a1aa26c0796290cccb5f",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 461
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "It isn't. You don't run anything yourself.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8bb9ea9157bf10cfc0412b82c3db2c446f18c923da674b11737712c12913e1dd",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 469
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "You add one line to your agent's config, and your agent gains the new search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9473dacc1c838277575e7362abbe2af9e530b26de991292dced03173d09cd8d4",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 476
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "The terminal stays untouched.\n\nHow do you give it to your agent?",
      "checksum": "sha256:88a83047f811b8bdcf7e85fcbf5d1de30556663af560b4927942a17a5da8139d",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 491
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Two minutes. For Claude Code, add one line to your config file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:43e69c04894ed8cb60b2c2515642815fad790655978576f7588d51ad236953d1",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 503
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "For Cursor, install the extension. Restart your agent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:46c4c8b8ea5a0249e88e5689731839b2a2c5f798a2dc779cc32f255bb24da01a",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 515
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Done. Your AI agent now searches code by structure \u2014 not by guessing at text.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2c361c775773181325b3e12eaed18d0fc53153bb0ea1a65ed1ce50b22746756d",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 523
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "That's the upgrade. So here's the question.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d1e01691aafa40a675757c0fbf2acbea3da8e808f98cbb9665acccfbe874476",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 538
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Your AI agent burns money on every refactor \u2014 one-hundred-and-twenty-two percent more work than it needs, on real code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0663646b5e2220967fe2f7586a052888d32d2c5e996cc834dfe23695c24bae5f",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 7.244625850340136,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 545
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "Are you fixing that today with one config line?",
      "checksum": "sha256:d74e798c9a344e37d477ce11141f06b838e1c39f989e3e894e937769abaab791",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 564
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Or accepting the waste? Drop your pick in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5221852b3b397ae42dc0a9f2b576c7b2a4fbe7021ed38257c6e47603b947cb2d",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 573
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "Subscribe for more AI coding deep-dives.",
      "checksum": "sha256:417ac33d25f7909da5b7c45fc4930677dc35ab07137530ce67c96a323464963d",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 583
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ed8ab98bd7df91d3b58e78eff21993418ad4b085b0557e8f6564adfb92975283",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 589
    }
  ]
}